courses.label: Frontend Name G20 EN
courses.description: Our most popular course which includes 20 lessons in small groups (up to 9 students) per week

courses.label: Exam prep Toefl
courses.description: Experience a detailed preparation for the TOEFL exam with us. The exam itself can only be booked externally: Booking.

accommodations.label: Homestay
accommodations.description: Enjoy your stay in one of our carefully selected host families. All of them have been working with us for many years.

accommodations.label: Residence
accommodations.description: Various residences are available in close proximity to our campus. The most modern accommodation coupled with personally selected furnishings refine your stay.

accommodations.label: Hotel
accommodations.description: Exclusive hotels of the best class are available for our students. Choose one of our well-designed rooms and enjoy your stay.

insurances.label: Health insurance
insurances.description: Our health insurance provides comprehensive coverage from the first day of benefits to the last. Accommodation in 1 - 2 bed rooms in case of hospitalization and repatriation in case of longer illness is included.

insurances.label: Theft insurance
insurances.description: Our theft insurance offers comprehensive assistance and unique service. Luggage, robbery and vandalism are included.

fees.label: Document Express Fee
fees.description: Guarantees the processing of all required documents within 12 hours.

fees.label: Parking fee
fees.description: Secure a parking space directly on the campus. No annoying search for a parking space or long walks to the campus.

fees.label: Regular mail
fees.description: Standard mail of the required documents - free of charge

activities.label: Hiking - Easy level of difficulty
activities.description: Hiking is one of the most effective forms of exercise. It is also a great way to enjoy cutural and leisure activities in the city. The Signed Seafront Healtwalk Route covers four miles of seafront between Hove Lagoon and Brighton Marina. Join our guided small group hiking tours to enjoy the nature and meeting other students.

activities.label: Hiking - Medium level of difficulty
activities.description: Devils Dyke Loop from Portslade Village Intermediate Hiking Tour. Enjoy 6 miles of hiking in one of our guided mini groups. Good fitness required. Mostly accessible paths. Sure-footedness required. The starting point of the Tour is accessible with public transport.

activities.label: Riding
activities.description: Padomy Riding Centre is a British Horse Society Approved Riding Centre offering private, semi private or class lessons as well as escorted rides and pony rides on a secluded lane. Cross country schooling is also available (weather permitting).  All lessons are held in our indoor school or outside on our all weather arena. Escorted rides take place along the bridleways in the beautiful West Sussex countryside around Arundel. Cross country schooling takes place in our cross country field.  Also offers pony parties!

activities.label: Cinema evening
activities.description: Join our free cinema evening available once per week in our large event room. Popcorn and a Coke included :-) Movies are changing weekly.

activities.label: City Sightseeing Tour
activities.description: Brighton City Sightseeing Tour takes you to visit one of the south-coast's most vibrant and popular resorts. This extravagant city offers many things to do and places to go, from the striking Royal Pavilion, Regency architecture, and Victorian aquariums, to the famous Brighton Pier, Sea Life!

activities.label: Cooking Experience
activities.description: Get the chance to learn how to cook some magnificent local cuisines. Different classes out there teach you how to make a great majority of different dishes, some offering special perks to the classes to make the experience even more enjoyable.

activities.label: Online Cooking Experience
activities.description: Corona Cooking: Get the chance to learn how to cook some delightful local cuisine. Various courses out there teach you how to make a vast majority of different dishes, some offer special discounts for the classes to make the experience even more enjoyable.
